---
// No props needed — content is static
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    {/* Header */}
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-sage-deep">
        Two ways to gather
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight text-ink mt-5 mb-4 leading-tight">
        Led by someone who <em class="italic text-rose">knows the way</em>.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-ink-soft text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Every circle on circles.love is run by a real person you can see and verify — whether they hold a clinical license or a coaching practice.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Cards */}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      
      {/* Therapy Card — Symptom-Relief Focus */}
      <a 
        href="/companions?orientation=symptom-relief" 
        class="group relative rounded-[22px] p-10 overflow-hidden border border-line bg-gradient-to-br from-[#EFF1EC] to-[#E7ECE5] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_18px_44px_rgba(42,33,53,0.08)] block no-underline"
      >
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sage-deep" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 mb-5 text-sage-deep" viewBox="0 0 46 46" fill="none">
          <circle cx="19" cy="23" r="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="27" cy="23" r="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        </svg>
        
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-normal tracking-tight text-ink mb-2">
          Therapy circles
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-sage-deep mb-4">
          Symptom-Relief Focus
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink-soft text-base leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Clinical and psychoeducational groups — grief, anxiety, ADHD, identity — run by licensed clinicians, in the states they're licensed to practice.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sage-deep" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none">
            <path d="m3 8 2.5 2.5L12 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          LCSW · LMFT · LPC · PsyD
          <span class="font-normal text-ink-soft">— verified license shown on every listing</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      {/* Healing Card — Values-Driven Exploration */}
      <a 
        href="/companions?orientation=values-driven" 
        class="group relative rounded-[22px] p-10 overflow-hidden border border-line bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FBF0E3] to-[#F7E9D8] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_18px_44px_rgba(42,33,53,0.08)] block no-underline"
      >
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7v10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 mb-5 text-amber" viewBox="0 0 46 46" fill="none">
          <circle cx="23" cy="23" r="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="23" cy="23" r="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.5"/>
        </svg>
        
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-normal tracking-tight text-ink mb-2">
          Healing circles
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-amber mb-4">
          Values-Driven Exploration
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink-soft text-base leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Coach- and facilitator-led circles — grief tending, life transitions, burnout, community — for support that doesn't need to be clinical to be real.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none">
            <path d="m3 8 2.5 2.5L12 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          Coaches · healers · facilitators
          <span class="font-normal text-ink-soft">— credentials and approach stated up front</span>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>